org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs

Class NFMT

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.AbstractStruct
      • org.openntf.domino.nsfdata.structs.NFMT
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Externalizable, java.io.Serializable

    public class NFMT
extends AbstractStruct
    This structure holds the format for character text number strings. You set up this structure based on the number format you want to use. Definitions for the various fields of this structure are found in NFMT_xxx and NATTR_xxx. (misc.h)
